  "texts": [
    "The first cluster in violet focuses on assessing the volatility of cryptocurrencies, specifically Bitcoin, while the second cluster in yellow focuses on the price discovery and market efficiency of Ethereum and the stablecoin, that is, Tether.",
    "The third cluster, in red, highlights the role of the volatility and liquidity of cryptocurrencies using highfrequency data.",
    "The fourth green cluster focuses on asymmetry in cryptocurrency futures.",
    "The fifth cluster in blue shows the safe haven ability of Bitcoin and gold during COVID-19.",
    "Co-citation analysis reveals the relationship between two papers if they are concurrently cited by a third (Small 1973)."
  ]
}